task.summary: Adding a quick factory to instantiate the Trans class
Adding a quick factory to instantiate the Trans class
Small bugfixes, and MvcTranslator set to default

Refactored to use gettext and its friends, rather than relying on the MvcTranslator to repeat strings into the Twig compiler. This means modifying your language configuration, but it is worth it. The performance gain is considerable.
